---
title: Cheddar Bacon Cheeseburger with Wedges and Roasted Garlic Slaw
description: This Cheddar Bacon Cheeseburger is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
